Silver Oak Connoisseur Gift Set
List.Description:
Inspired by the most reputable and sought after wineries in the world, this collection is for anyone who appreciates fine wine. The heart of this gift is two wines created under the leadership of the Duncan family - Silver Oak and Twomey Cellars. Silver Oak crafts complex and elegant Cabernet Sauvignon, while Twomey creates exquisite Merlot. Paired with top shelf wine accessories including a Riedel Cabernet Decanter, Built-NY two bottle tote and Screwpull corkscrew, this is the ultimate gift for the discriminating wine connoisseur.

This gift includes:

  • Silver Oak Alexander Cabernet Sauvignon
  • Twomey Merlot
  • Rieldel Cabernet Decanter
  • Screwpull Table Model corkscrew
  • BUILT NY red 2-bottle soft tote

Wine gift sets & baskets may be packaged with the bottles separately boxed for their protection during shipment

Pursuant to state laws in New York, gifts that contain both food and wine will be sent in two separate packages.

Final Touch Ice Wine Chiller
List.Description:
This wine bottle chiller is too cool... it's a wine cooler made of ice! It not only keeps your wine chilled but is also a great conversation piece. Simple to use: Fill the mold with water and place in freezer for 24 hours. After 24 hours, remove ice from the mold and display on stainless-steel stand. The Ice Bottle Chiller will last 6 hours as a bottle chiller. You can even decorate the ice sculpture by placing items such as berries or flowers in the water before freezing.

Wine not included.
